snippet: Sylvia Fowles had 21 points and 9 rebounds, and Maya Moore 19 points and 8 rebounds for Minnesota, which prevailed at home in Game 2 against the Indiana Fever.
abstract: Minnesota Lynx defeat Indiana Fever, 77-71, to tie WNBA Finals, 2-2.
lead_paragraph: Sylvia Fowles had 21 points and 9 rebounds, and Maya Moore 19 points and 8 rebounds for Minnesota, which prevailed at home in Game 2 against the Indiana Fever.

headline.print_headline: Led by Fowles and Moore, the Lynx Pull Even
headline.main: Led by Fowles, Lynx Pull Even in W.N.B.A. Finals
